    <div class="reviews-grid">
      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p class="review-text">&ldquo;We have a slow combustion heater that gets used hard every winter. David cleaned the flue and found significant creosote build-up and a partially blocked baffle. Heater runs so much better now — really glad we called.&rdquo;</p><p class="review-author">Wayne D., Cranbourne</p></div>
      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p class="review-text">&ldquo;Bought our home and had no idea when the open fireplace was last serviced. David inspected and cleaned the full system, removed a bird nest and gave a clear verbal report. Great service.&rdquo;</p><p class="review-author">Michelle T., Cranbourne</p></div>
      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p class="review-text">&ldquo;Quick to respond, professional and thorough. David swept the chimney and pointed out a damaged cap that was letting rainwater into the flue. Something we would never have spotted ourselves. Highly recommend.&rdquo;</p><p class="review-author">Scott R., Cranbourne</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
